{"tid":2028744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇完先討論] 當你想放棄時 唔該你自已睇番呢段片","createTime":"2020-05-22T03:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:21:22.000Z","uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b313443e92b48e735c1944e9983b37c64d3527fc","tid":2028744,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o1FgvWBwgDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo1FgvWBwgDU&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=4c78d49b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o1FgvWBwgDU</a><br />\n<br />\n唔洗多講 要明既就會明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6944e5ebc26432ea13d8394c505caeed1c3de5d","tid":2028744,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiJO5UK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiJO5UK.jpg&h=7797c282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【如果你覺得好無力，不妨諗下...難道習近平又過得好好？】<br />\n<br />\n「黎明前嘅黑暗係最黑暗」係句好詩意嘅說話。如果通俗少少講，就係：有打開機都知，隻boss開始暴走放大招嘅時候，其實就係佢殘血就死之時。<br />\n中共之所以呢個時候推國安法，唔係因為佢管治能力有幾高明或者幾有作為，而係相反，正正顯示到佢地已經冇招。一個喺管治上已經無招可用嘅政權，敗亡亦不過係時候問題。"}]}